#23912
broker dealer hooded figure merchant~
The Veil Broker~
The Veil Broker lingers here, watching everything with quiet interest.
~
Draped in layered, dark robes that seem to absorb the surrounding
light, the Veil Broker stands with unnatural stillness. His face
is obscured beneath a deep hood, but faint glimmers of pale light
flicker where his eyes should be.
Thin, gloved fingers idly trace invisible patterns in the air, as
though counting something only he can see. Small trinkets like 
coins, shards, and fragments of unknown originhang from his
belt, each giving off a faint, unnatural hum.
When you draw near, his head tilts ever so slightly, acknowledging
your presence before you speak. You get the sense he already knows
why youre here and whether youre worth his time.
~
