#23917
engine refraction echo~
The Refraction Engine~
The engine pulses with its crystalline form with energy
~
A towering lattice of shifting crystal floats at the center of the
chamber, its many facets refracting light into impossible angles.
Within its core, distorted shapes press outward. Faces frozen in silent
screams, limbs reaching toward freedom, identities stripped of meaning.

The structure hums with relentless purpose, drawing in fragments of 
reality and compressing them into dense, radiant forms. Each pulse 
tightens the lattice, refining what it has taken into something 
tangible something valuable.

It does not think.
It does not feel.
It only refines.
~
